metadata.name: Daonnaki #1
metadata.description: The Daonnaki is a collection of 10,000 alien inspired 3D art! The aim of the Daonnaki is to bring futuristic technology to the WEB3 space to enable project founders and holders to manage their communities in a more efficient & effective manner. Daonnaki is the governing digital collection which runs the power of the WEB3 tools that the NFTsociety platform offers! -Allowlist for new collections -Transparent and fair giveaways -DAO governance for new and minted collections -Launchad for not yet minted collections.More about the platform - https://wp.nftsociety.io All royalties go to a DAO wallet!
